org.jtransfo

Class AbstractSetTypeConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jtransfo.AbstractSetTypeConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Named, NeedsJTransfo, TypeConverter<Set,Set>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AutomaticSetTypeConverter, SetTypeConverter

    public abstract class AbstractSetTypeConverter
extends Object
implements TypeConverter<Set,Set>, Named, NeedsJTransfo
    Abstract type converter for Set objects. You need to define the to object contents for the set.

      • setKeepNullSet

        public void setKeepNullSet(boolean keepNullSet)
        Set whether null values should be kept (true). When false (which is the default value), an empty set is set.
        Parameters:

      • setAlwaysNewSet

        public void setAlwaysNewSet(boolean alwaysNewSet)
        Set whether a new set should be used as container for the values. When false the set is reused if not null.
        Parameters:
